# .mailmap — canonicalizes commit-author identities for `git log`/`git shortlog`/
# `git blame` (with --use-mailmap, the default for shortlog) and for GitHub's
# aggregate Contributors graph. It does NOT change the author shown on individual
# commit pages on github.com, nor does it rewrite history.
